MediaInfoDll Help File

 Welcome

MediaInfoDll Help File

Plugin Name:

MediaInfoDll

Current Version:

0.5.0.0

Description:

This plugin allow to get the info from a lot of media files using MediaInfo dll and Memory plugin.

Author:

Danixu

Web:

http://www.amsspecialist.info

E-mail:

laordentemplariaes@gmail.com

Requirements:

Memory Plugin and Autoplay Media Studio 8

Copyright:

2011
